<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/2211723-why-was-the-quayles-child-stillborn-is">Why was the Quayles&#39; child stillborn? Is it because Tessa took Dypraxa?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_2211723'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F19000.The_Constant_Gardener">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/2211723-why-was-the-quayles-child-stillborn-is">4 months ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/2211723-why-was-the-quayles-child-stillborn-is">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/20738920-orinoco-womble-tidy-bag-and-all"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1406361683i/20738920._UX100_CR0,18,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/20738920-orinoco-womble-tidy-bag-and-all">Orinoco Womble (tidy bag and all)</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
There is nothing in the book to indicate that Tessa ever took Dypraxa, which is meant to be a remedy for tuberculosis. 
</span>
</div>
</div>
