<span id="freeTextContainer6346986836828558040">What a great read! Le Carré takes on Big Pharma, government agencies, and a whole lot of other things corrupt, and he does so without sugarcoating it with the ‘justice is served’ ending that Hollywood tacked onto an otherwise excellent adaptation. I thought the movie was wonderful, but it pales into insignificance when placed next to this.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


