<li class='cover' id='bookCover_12806802'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/12806802-the-honourable-schoolboy-by-john-le-carre-summary-study-guide"><img alt="The Honourable Schoolboy by John le Carre Summary  Study Guide" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442876226l/12806802._SX98_.jpg" />
